Usage: set_offchip_package_trace [-help] -reset  | {-name <string> -ploc_file_list <string> -spice <string> -mapping <string> [-subckt <string>] }

-help                        # Prints out the command usage
-mapping <string>            # <mapping file> (string, required)
-name <string>               # <trace model name> (string, required)
-ploc_file_list <string>     # <list of bump location file> (string, required)
-reset                       # <reset all previous set_offchip_package_trace
                             # commands> (bool, optional)
-spice <string>              # <Spice model> (string, required)
-subckt <string>             # <top level sub-circuit name> (string, optional)